overview:
Quotes are any phrase or phrases said by any person, known or unknown, that exist because they’re being remembered and written down. Anything anyone says worth mentioning is to be quoted.

Whenever you have a phrase on your mind or a thought that you need to share, make it a personal quote and everyone can let you know what they think about it.

Next to famous, popular, funny, love quotes, you can find personal quotes from quote-reviewers. You can also become a quote-reviewer and create a famous quote.
